text: Zhao Xisha (, born 28 September 1992) is a Chinese professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . She is from Hebei. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cyclists Category:Cyclists from Hebei
